Class ImportCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • goal.parser.ParsedObject
      • goal.util.ImportCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IParsedObject, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ParsedObject>

    public class ImportCommand
extends ParsedObject
    Wrapper for the data from an #import-command. Stores the path as stored in the agent file, as well as the actual referenced file, along with a record of where the command is located in the agent file.
    Author:
    N.Kraayenbrink
